			<description><![CDATA[<div>Muslim Apologists like <a href="https://muslimskeptic.com/author/drjou/">Daniel Haquiqajou</a> come up with excuses like (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_El13YXwRDM&amp;t=2753s">Video link</a>):</div>
<ul>
<li>Marriage and sex with 9 years old pre-pubescent girl was a 'tradition' of that era. </li>
<li>In the vast majority of history, life expectancy was relatively low. Moreover, infant mortality was considerably high.</li>
<li>Thus, it was then necessary to use the extent of the 'fertility window' for reproduction. </li>
